 />\n她丈夫把她送院後，醫生要為一度心跳停頓的她進行心肺復蘇，之後診斷出她患上急性高鈉血症。伯納德指，她體內大量的納吸去了她肌肉和器官的水份，腦部亦出現脫水，使她患上腦橋中央髓鞘溶解症，即部分神經細胞受損。四天後，雖然病人可以睜眼，但四肢已癱瘓、無法吞嚥和有言語障礙。<br />\n伯納德指，正常人根本無法飲下大量豉油而不嘔吐。他認為病人原是患有「乳糜瀉」，進食麩質後會出現幻覺；但因一直被誤診患精神病，令情況加劇，終使她精神錯亂至暴飲豉油。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T16:25:51.000Z","msg":"片<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QiBpKuTrFrw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQiBpKuTrFrw&d=gMp4lm1kVIaKzDSdPOjQ4L%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=67b594bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QiBpKuTrFrw</a>"},{"pid":"83bb1a1e45dc85edb761a91e9a788c358d069d0b","tid":943761,"uid":12000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T16:50:18.000Z","msg":"聽何蛇講用咖啡灌腸咪無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bd60a1c1dd8426dd8bc606d3d088ed32d9f6afd","tid":943761,"uid":61282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed654a98da926434fc27047157ccdba74af4a768","tid":943761,"uid":33077,"like":89,"dislike":4,"score":85,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T00:17:02.000Z","msg":"他認為病人原是患有「乳糜瀉」，進食麩質後會出現幻覺<br />\n<br />\non9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T16:57:38.000Z","msg":"?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"329f34d4dcae80d61deac64a28d803c4d6e6c387","tid":943761,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T17:55:38.000Z","msg":"豆漿就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d93379891c81b28f26ab3940fca29e4b20f6a4f","tid":943761,"uid":50193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T17:57:49.000Z","msg":"自然淘汰姐"},{"pid":"28238f6cd99601e14645543a0e4dfc7f2cf9f3a0","tid":943761,"uid":57700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T18:02:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}